{"tid":917690,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"90後TG谷 吹水鳩up食好西 唱k飲油踩單車","createTime":"2018-11-26T15:04:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-13T04:34:21.000Z","uid":74339,"like":2,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6bd8620c9766c5f76f876e51fafca8211ab1afa8","tid":917690,"uid":74339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T15:04:19.000Z","msg":"召集90後既自摸奶奶。開左未夠一個月，搵班岩傾既入嚟吹水鳩up、一齊出去玩。歡迎任何合法活動，谷友可以隨便發起任何聚會。如果你有咩想做又搵唔到人陪你就快啲入嚟啦。<br />\n<br />\n暫時搞過以下活動<br />\n唱k<br />\n飲酒<br />\nChill drink<br />\n打邊爐<br />\n宵夜<br />\nBoardgame <br />\n<br />\n嚟緊會有行山<br />\n<br />\n填左form既等等，大概一星期加一次人，會有揀人<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSccf6tCuqnNpuWbLz9VsOhLSyrWvNMja9_x5wAoP5GW-03YHw/viewform?usp=pp_url\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSccf6tCuqnNpuWbLz9VsOhLSyrWvNMja9_x5wAoP5GW-03YHw%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dpp_url&d=N%2FH%2FOvxDEl%2Bi%2FUGdY79q1C7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=854e0fff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSccf6tCuqnNpuWbLz9VsOhLSyrWvNMja9_x5wAoP5GW-03YHw/viewform?usp=pp_url</a>"},{"pid":"d72e76ffb55772242df304045d4334da7b7c41f5","tid":917690,"uid":44503,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T15:05:23.000Z","msg":"有咩油好飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdb63b980a9b8c0b448e08b7c895b4c35eb43f69","tid":917690,"uid":74339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d72e76ffb55772242df304045d4334da7b7c41f5","tid":917690,"uid":44503,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T15:05:23.000Z","msg":"有咩油好飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T15:06:38.000Z","msg":"我最鍾意鼓油同蠔油，唔飲得辣油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f154bb41725676acba10b999ec9bcf8aab8903fa","tid":917690,"uid":44503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b